DESCRIPTION:Tyron Asphy\, founder of&#160\;Japan-American Butokukan Kara
 te Association\, has returned to the Langston Hughes Performing Arts Ins
 titute\, where he taught community karate classes over 40 years ago.<br>
 <br>Tyron works with five instructors to offer martial arts classes to s
 tudents ages 5 to 75 years old. His commitment to bringing access to dis
 cipline\, flexibility\, and self-defense to the Black youth and other re
 sidents in the Central District area is invaluable to the overall health
  and well-being of our community.
