 essions are facilitated by Tina LaPadula\, Arts Education Project Manage
 r from the Seattle Office of Arts &amp\; Culture\, Rayna Mathis\, The Cr
 eative Advantage Project Manager for Seattle Public Schools\, and member
 s of The Creative Advantage Implementation Team.<br><br>Register here an
 d you will receive a Teams Link in your confirmation email.
