DESCRIPTION:The Public Art Advisory Committee (PAAC) serves to review an
 d recommend public art projects and programs\, develop and amend the Mun
 icipal Art Plan\, and advocate for percent-for-art projects in public/pr
 ivate partnerships. The PAAC operates\, promotes\, and supports the deve
 lopment of art in public places including parks\, libraries\, community 
 centers\, roadways\, bridges\, and other public venues to enrich citizen
 s&#39\; daily lives and give voice to artists.
