 h the YMCA&#39\;s &quot\;Get Engaged&quot\; program.<br><br><strong>Miss
 ion</strong><br>The Seattle Arts Commission supports the City by advocat
 ing for arts policy\, creating access for equitable participation in the
  arts\, and fostering enriching arts engagement for all residents.
